846?dgcid=coauthor" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;sciencedirect.com/science/arti&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;cle/pii/S0896627323005846?dgcid=coauthor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/110/996/859/988/940/646/original/4cc195722add8a7f.png"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/110/996/859/988/940/646/original/4cc195722add8a7f.png" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110996856674913555</guid><pubDate>Sat, 02 Sep 2023 18:00:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Manlio De Domenico</title><link>https://mathstodon.xyz/@manlius/110997071841512849</link><description>Ouch! May the force be with me.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/110/997/071/924/340/403/original/2baaf705e4b56806.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/110/997/071/924/340/403/original/2baaf705e4b56806.jpg" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110997071983233000</guid><pubDate>Sat, 02 Sep 2023 18:55:05 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Carl Zimmer</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@Carl_Zimmer/110997804795587947</link><description>TFW you turn in a book manuscript&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/media_attachments/files/110/997/804/506/832/676/original/fbad77fae556abfe.jpeg"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/media_attachments/files/110/997/804/506/832/676/original/fbad77fae556abfe.jpeg" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110997804795587947</guid><pubDate>Sat, 02 Sep 2023 22:01:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Manlio De Domenico</title><link>https://mathstodon.xyz/@manlius/111001106297539795</link><description>I'll be hones